At Plantyn, Liber* and Leya the digital environment are perceived quite positive, but so is thecompetition

In the Netherlands, thedigital environmentaccounts for quite somenegativity, although this is the same for the competition

We need to fill in hygiene-needs in ease-of-use in order to ensure digital adoption and user satisfaction
